---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Forms and documents
intro: "Download the forms and documents you need. If you can't find what you're looking for, please contact us."
description: "Download patient forms and documents from Scoonie Medical Practice — registration, medical records requests, and more."
breadcrumb:
  - label: About us
    url: /about/
  - label: Forms and documents
---

<div class="max-w-3xl">

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">

    {% set formsList = [forms.registration, forms.consent, forms["subject-access"], forms["pelvic-health"]] %}
    {% for form in formsList %}
    <div class="service-card">
      <h2 class="service-card__title text-base">{{ form.title }}</h2>
      <p class="service-card__desc">{{ form.description }}</p>
      {% if form.file %}
      <a href="{{ form.file }}" class="btn btn--primary text-sm mt-3" download>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5M16.5 12L12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3"/></svg>
        Download PDF
      </a>
      {% else %}
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-mid mt-3 italic">PDF coming soon — please ask at reception.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}

  </div>

  <div class="prose-content mt-8">
    <h2>Private work, forms, and letters</h2>
    <p>We provide a range of private services including medical reports, insurance forms, and letters for employers, solicitors, and other organisations. These are not covered by the NHS and are charged at a standard rate.</p>
    <p>Our current fee for private work is <strong>&pound;186 per hour</strong> (pro rata for shorter items). Fees are in line with the British Medical Association's suggested rates.</p>
    <p>Common requests include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Fitness-to-travel letters</li>
      <li>Insurance and mortgage medical reports</li>
      <li>Employer medical certificates (beyond the standard fit note)</li>
      <li>Solicitor reports</li>
      <li>Passport countersigning</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please allow up to 4 weeks for completion. Fees are payable in advance. Ask at reception or <a href="/contact/get-in-touch/">contact us</a> for more information.</p>
  </div>

</div>
